eam，食榴槤，糖水）<br />\n總之玩d味濃，又難清潔嘅嘢食<br />\n7.玩蟲<br />\n8.玩水槍射顏色水<br />\n9紙飛機<br />\n10.煙霧彈，煙餅<br />\n<br />\n我明白現實情況不利真勇武<br />\n應該玩下小學雞式惡作劇<br />\n諗下之前返中小學<br />\n一定有d最百厭嘅同學點樣上堂搞事<br />\n令到佢開唔到會就得"},{"pid":"00d59372c7bebbb3bf230bf54aed06c7b5283313","tid":2021900,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:37:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f612a4a596b37b49041e59bce9e8d753791b1315","tid":2021900,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66596a74ac4a85bade60e27906021282e07af550","tid":2021900,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:43:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2c9e2605333ce669a1bee805f1fbc64b57605c7","tid":2021900,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"077a66afde42d2877a244e7dd903eceb90865461","tid":2021900,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5e6f2aeb1aaad7a5ba007c05f4cd4fb20ca425","tid":2021900,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"繼續努力"},{"pid":"c4a5f8d0b5784a066f46b04ca69e5dc138854ab7","tid":2021900,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"樓主問個咁問題？<br />\n但蟲太直頭坐左係處咩都唔做<br />\n<br />\n咁又收唔收蟲太今日既貨？"}]}